For every additional element, why you are adding it?
-We added fire-wall to prevent incoming threat by filtering incoming traffic in the network.
-Adding SSL helps to encrypt traffic between client and web server.
-We added monitor to help collect data from various component.

What are firewalls for?
-To help prevent incoming threat by filtering incoming traffic in the network.

Why is the traffic served over HTTPS?
-It ensures data confidentiality, integrity, and authenticity, enhancing the security of the website and user interactions.

What monitoring is used for?
-it helps in tracking the health performance of the infrastructure

How the monitoring tool is collecting data?
-It helps in collecting data by capturing events from server and other component

Explain what to do if you want to monitor your web server QPS?
-You will configure the monitoring tool to capture related incoming http requests.

Why terminating SSL at the load balancer level is an issue?
-It will exposes sensitive data to an unauthorized access.

